@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Route Handler\nPOST /api/movies/{movieId}/reviews" as Route
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth
participant "Review Service" as Service
participant "Review Repository" as Repository
database "Supabase DB\nreviews, movies" as Database

User -> Frontend: 리뷰 작성
Frontend -> Route: POST /api/movies/{movieId}/reviews
Route -> Auth: 현재 세션 확인

alt 인증된 사용자
    Auth --> Route: userId 반환
    Route -> Service: 리뷰 작성 요청
    Service -> Repository: 영화 존재 여부 확인
    Repository -> Database: movies 조회
    Database --> Repository: movie row
    Service -> Repository: 리뷰 저장
    Repository -> Database: reviews insert
    Database --> Repository: review row
    Repository --> Service: 저장된 리뷰
    Service --> Route: 리뷰 작성 결과
    Route --> Frontend: 201 Created
    Frontend --> User: 작성된 리뷰 표시
else 인증되지 않은 사용자
    Auth --> Route: 세션 없음
    Route --> Frontend: 401 Unauthorized
    Frontend --> User: 로그인 필요 상태 표시
end
@enduml
